/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你返西伯利亞拉雪橇啦</blockquote><br />\n廢青俾我踩親條尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n講緊事實，個個都做經理文員，咁邊個洗碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4c1415ca81f4f2430a0bef4aa038b6273d54d7","tid":415262,"uid":59559,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:00:42.000Z","msg":"如果8小時5天工作二萬<br />\n大把人掙住做啦<br />\n政府就係幫住啲商家"},{"pid":"16cafb155fc071bafa72c7a4359e9103a1f2be9c","tid":415262,"uid":60279,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:05:13.000Z","msg":"重點:<br />\n<br />\n1. 本地居民--&gt;為左買樓--&gt;努力工作---&gt;樓價係咁升--&gt;買唔起<br />\n2. 本地垃圾--&gt;想買樓--&gt;唔做野---&gt;囉綜援---&gt;反而有樓派比佢<br />\n3. 外奴---&gt;黎HK為左錢---&gt;政府因為人地遠離原居地--&gt;派樓比佢<br />\n<br />\n結果: 努力做野反而無樓, 不能達至目標, 推動力下降, 成為2, 最後成為借口比政府推出3<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結: 政府垃撚圾"},{"pid":"1ad227beae5fa155a24696b4fa2ab0ee2842dc11","tid":415262,"uid":21432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:05:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>勞動力下降係事實，香港正係步台灣後塵<br />\n但係唔代表要輪入外勞，不如推出政策鼓<del>勵</del>吹班年輕傻鳩去做勞動階層，好過佢地日日發皇帝夢，以為自己有機會發圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你返西伯利亞拉雪橇啦</blockquote><br />\n廢青俾我踩親條尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n講緊事實，個個都做經理文員，咁邊個洗碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你兩句就踩到條尾，你估個個似你做狗咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗眼看人咪人人係狗囉<br />\n<br />\n無人洗咪你去洗囉，西伯利亞狗洗碗分分鐘做埋狗明星添"},{"pid":"463be6def45f3bd3dba163e7e1cf6ec83da08dc1","tid":415262,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/090900_6cd58ef90ec30ccb0d3bb5051935892c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F090900_6cd58ef90ec30ccb0d3bb5051935892c.jpg&h=9b058770&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/090901_b8d67519805b3dabae722c54c77ef543.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F090901_b8d67519805b3dabae722c54c77ef543.jpg&h=e42bca31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/090902_820262c13756f430f9a0c905d52f4bd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F090902_820262c13756f430f9a0c905d52f4bd4.jpg&h=229e2042&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/090905_57a66f43241685e3723f26be1ab5f9e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F090905_57a66f43241685e3723f26be1ab5f9e8.jpg&h=db592ce2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/090906_aa33d05828f299ac592613b55ea9c132.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F090906_aa33d05828f299ac592613b55ea9c132.jpg&h=630918cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1f5f040f87e7fd37f39982cdd4b06a18d1b87e6","tid":415262,"uid":33848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:10:20.000Z","msg":"其他西方國家avg. workweek 係 35 hours咁上下<br />\n我就當你單計勞動人口可能會再多少少<br />\n點都唔及香港<br />\n你好彩唔洗6日, 再好彩唔洗5日半, 再好彩唔洗長短周<br />\n番5日己經係講緊45 hours<br />\n我成日都唔明點解勞動力唔夠"},{"pid":"ae01dfd262966e81e4ef0780dd7b59d2bbffc70d","tid":415262,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:10:55.000Z","msg":"自由市場嘛，<br />